name: ExtensionDeviceDispense
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.DeviceDispense` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `DeviceDispense` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `DeviceDispense` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`DeviceDispense` 0..* `DeviceDispense`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
* R5 `DeviceDispense` 0..* `DeviceDispense`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `DeviceDispense` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `DeviceDispense` is not mapped.
